# Local Claude session state (never committed to the repo).
.claude/

# One-off visual-review screenshots saved to the repo root by the
# Playwright MCP browser tool. Numbered PNGs / YMLs (01-home.png …)
# are disposable artifacts of an in-session visual audit.
/[0-9][0-9]-*.png
/[0-9][0-9]-*.yml
# Lighthouse CI cached run artifacts (large per-route lhr-*.json/.html files,
# regenerated on each lhci run; never useful to commit).
.lighthouseci/

